{"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [], "create_time": 1646730170, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1646730170, "likenum": 1, "n_attentions": 1, "n_comments": 0, "pid": 16743, "poll": {"answers": [{"option": "赞", "votes": 1}, {"option": "踩", "votes": 0}, {"option": "路过", "votes": 0}], "vote": null}, "reply": 0, "text": "#报时 **北京时间 2022-03-08 17:00**\n\n>多年后，我终于成就了自己。然而可惜不是你，陪我到最后\n>　　　　　　　　——《原创》", "timestamp": 1646730170}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [], "create_time": 1646729668, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1646729668, "likenum": 2, "n_attentions": 2, "n_comments": 0, "pid": 16742, "poll": null, "reply": 0, "text": "可能是高中养成习惯了，一点点都不想写作业怎么办啊😭", "timestamp": 1646729668}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 45100, "create_time": 1646739329, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "……", "timestamp": 1646739329}], "create_time": 1646729165, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1646739329, "likenum": 20, "n_attentions": 20, "n_comments": 1, "pid": 16741, "poll": null, "reply": 1, "text": "（转）外行和内行眼中相差最大的职业有哪些？\n\n1. 部委和京沪公务员\n外行眼中是金饭碗，内行知道才一万多点月薪，比初中毕业的快递小哥、送外卖小哥高不到哪里去。公务员待遇最高的是深圳和苏州，根本就不是部委和京沪。\n2. 部委下属的事业单位\n员工听起来是体制内，跟部委公务员工资差不多低，但部委公务员按照级别工作很多年后分房，事业单位只能眼巴巴看着别人分房。 \n 3. 四大银行总行员工\n外行眼中是特大银行总部，内行知道四大银行总行员工平均才20来万年薪，待遇和个人发展都远不如名气没这么大的40-70万年薪的前十名的地方股份制商业银行，而且四大银行总行关系户众多。\n  4. 美国名校终身教授\n被外行顶礼膜拜，内行知道这行性价比太低，投入巨大，要世界名校博士，博士毕业还要恶性内卷花十几年甚至几十年的时间做出超一流的科研成果才能当上美国名校正教授。但收获相对于投入却很有限，哈佛大学的正教授才22万美元年薪，副教授才18万美元年薪。还不如有名的脱口秀艺人、网红、主播、歌手、演员一天的收入，和企业家比更是成百上千倍的差距。付出了著名创业成功者的努力，却只收获了中产的薪水。  \n5. 著名土木设计院土木工程师\n外行眼中是铁饭碗，内行知道这行性价比太低，加班比996还狠，待遇只和部委或京沪公务员差不多，还没有分房。\n6. 军工央企下属的各大研究所\n军工利润被限制，发钱有国资委的工资总额限制。最差的工作之一。名校的工科研究生只能拿冷门专业的薪水", "timestamp": 1646729165}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [], "create_time": 1646729151, "cw": "xxg", "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1646729151, "likenum": 2, "n_attentions": 2, "n_comments": 0, "pid": 16740, "poll": null, "reply": 0, "text": "没有女菩萨的树洞，总是感觉少了些什么", "timestamp": 1646729151}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 45717, "create_time": 1646799923, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "应该是的，我们系的几个留学生上网课上了两年，入学后就没有来过…", "timestamp": 1646799923}], "create_time": 1646728851, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1646799923, "likenum": 4, "n_attentions": 4, "n_comments": 1, "pid": 16739, "poll": null, "reply": 1, "text": "疫情防控这几年是不是境外的留学生都进不来啊", "timestamp": 1646728851}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": null, "create_time": 1646728561, "cw": "性相关", "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1646751783, "likenum": 8, "n_attentions": 8, "n_comments": 6, "pid": 16738, "poll": null, "reply": 6, "text": "列表里的一个nps脱单了，不知道她会不会跟新男友讲自己的性经历，讲讲怎么被前男友调教的，讲讲自己yp的经历。\n啧啧，我也是够黑暗的。", "timestamp": 1646728561}, {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false